cdse_client (Go CLI)
====================

Go command-line client for the CaumeDSE REST API.  Provides encrypted secret
storage, encrypted CSV databases, user/org info, and audit log retrieval.
Runs in one-shot mode (single command per invocation) or interactively.


CONTENTS
========
I.    Prerequisites
II.   Build
